<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9872</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17581</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很久以前，一个小山村里住着一个老汉和他的三个儿子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17583</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21095</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第一个儿子又高又瘦。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21096</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24885</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二个儿子又矮又肥。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24886</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28319</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第三个儿子介于两者之间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28320</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31771</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老汉很爱他的儿子们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31772</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是有一点他不喜欢。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34519</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38045</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他不喜欢他们的懒惰。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38046</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43192</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老汉用尽了办法激励他的儿子们工作。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43193</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47391</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他告诉他们，他们会变得很富有。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47392</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51950</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他告诉他们，他们会娶到漂亮的新娘。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51951</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57251</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他告诉他们，他们年老时会很幸福和自豪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61724</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，懒儿子们从来不听劝告。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61725</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65227</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们对工作完全不感兴趣。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65228</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67939</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第一个儿子爱说话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67940</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70642</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二个儿子爱吃。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70643</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73802</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第三个儿子爱喝酒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73803</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78069</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们都觉得工作很无聊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78070</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83799</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很多年过去了，这三个懒儿子还住在家里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83800</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87012</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>高个儿的儿子还是很瘦。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87013</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90144</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>矮个儿的儿子越来越胖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90145</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93489</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第三个儿子秃顶了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93490</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101227</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老汉很老了，身体也很虚弱，没有什么力气去工作了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101228</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108906</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的农场得不到打理，葡萄园开始变得荒芜。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108907</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114382</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一天晚上，老汉把三个儿子叫进房间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114383</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121946</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“儿子们，我很老了，身体很虚弱，也很疲惫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121947</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124629</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我活不了多久了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124630</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129712</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我死前有件事必须告诉你们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129713</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136414</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我在葡萄园里藏了一个特别的东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136415</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141517</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>找到了就是你们的了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老汉当晚就去世了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145453</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150104</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天早上，他的儿子们议论了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150105</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156396</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第一个儿子问，“你们觉得父亲在葡萄园藏了什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156397</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159616</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不知道。”第二个儿子说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159616</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166306</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是肯定是他多年以前放在那里的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164626</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174221</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这些年来他已经太老了，又虚弱又疲惫，不可能再到葡萄园里去了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174222</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177647</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我同意。”第一个儿子说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177647</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183704</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是你们觉得那会是什么呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181773</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183974</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第三个儿子猜道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183975</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190180</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那肯定是钱，很多钱。这个农场曾经很富足。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190181</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196014</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果我们能找到那笔钱，我们就再也不用工作了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196015</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199934</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>于是，儿子们立刻行动了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199935</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206288</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们清除了葡萄园里疯长的野草，灌木和其他植物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206289</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208642</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后开始挖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208643</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216172</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每个人都挖得很快，因为他们都想成为第一个找到宝藏的人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216173</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221411</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>几年过去了，儿子们还是没有找到宝藏。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221412</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224825</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是儿子们都有了变化。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224826</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230620</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第一个儿子很高很壮，他不再是皮包骨头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230621</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235916</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二个儿子的体重减轻了不少，他不再肥胖了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235917</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241927</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第三个儿子还是秃顶，但是他看起来不再衰老，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241928</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246033</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为努力工作而变得更加健康了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246049</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每个儿子都娶到了一个美丽的新娘。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252743</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>还有另外一个变化。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252744</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260113</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>由于葡萄园得到了兄弟们的打理和照料，农场再次繁荣起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260114</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264771</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>懒儿子们变得富有了，但不是因为宝藏。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264772</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268912</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>财富来源于他们自己的辛勤劳动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268913</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>279478</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>从那之后，他们都生活得非常快乐。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>